text: Colobothea subcincta is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Laporte in 1840. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Colobothea subcincta. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1840
